le="vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap">(b) Initial support for importing data with custom date formats has been added in</span></p></li><li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type:circle;font-family:Arial;color:rgb(0,0,0);vertical-align:baseline;background-color:transparent"><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.48295454545455;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt"><span style="vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap">(b) We’ve added in the following console tools, </span></p></li><ul style="margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt"><li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type:square;font-family:Arial;color:rgb(0,0,0);vertical-align:baseline;background-color:transparent"><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.48295454545455;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt"><span style="color:rgb(51,51,51);vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;background-color:rgb(235,235,235)">bin/ushahidi dataprovider</span><span style="vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap"> for sending and receiving messages</span></p></li><li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type:square;font-family:Arial;color:rgb(0,0,0);vertical-align:baseline;background-color:transparent"><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.48295454545455;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:12pt"><span style="color:rgb(51,51,51);vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;background-color:rgb(235,235,235)">bin/tests</span><span style="vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap"> for running the entire API test suite</span></p></li></ul></ul></ul><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.15;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt"><span style="font-family:Arial;color:rgb(0,0,0);vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;background-color:transparent">Have a look at </span><a href="https://github.com/ushahidi/platform/releases/tag/v3.0.0-beta.10" style="text-decoration:none"><span style="font-family:Arial;text-decoration:underline;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;background-color:transparent">our release notes</span></a><span style="font-family:Arial;color:rgb(255,0,0);vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;background-color:transparent"> </span><span style="font-family:Arial;color:rgb(0,0,0);vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;background-color:transparent">and </span><a href="http://wp.me/p4vfAA-4iQ" style="text-decoration:none"><span style="font-family:Arial;text-decoration:underline;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;background-color:transparent">blog post announcement</span></a><span style="font-family:Arial;color:rgb(0,0,0);vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;background-color:transparent"> for more details on changes in this release. </span></p><h2 dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.15;margin-top:10pt;margin-bottom:0pt"><span style="font-family:&#39;Trebuchet MS&#39;;color:rgb(0,0,0);vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;background-color:transparent"><font>How can you help?</font></span></h2><h3 dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.15;margin-top:8pt;margin-bottom:0pt"><span style="font-family:&#39;Trebuchet MS&#39;;color:rgb(102,102,102);vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;background-color:transparent"><font>Developers</font></span></h3><ul style="margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt"><li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type:disc;font-family:Arial;color:rgb(0,0,0);vertical-align:baseline;background-color:transparent"><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.15;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt"><a href="https://github.com/ushahidi/platform/releases/tag/v3.0.0-beta.10" style="text-decoration:none"><span style="text-decoration:underline;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;background-color:transparent">Download</span></a><span style="vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;background-color:transparent"> and </span><a href="https://wiki.ushahidi.com/display/WIKI/Installing+Ushahidi+3.x" style="text-decoration:none"><span style="text-decoration:underline;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;background-color:transparent">Install the platform</span></a></p></li><li dir="ltr" style="